{
  "stem": "3964.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I don't recall it for sure, but I believe this hall was very close to a railroad station.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They march us out, and everybody there were told-- everybody hold onto their suitcases.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They marched us out to this railway station, or to railroad cars-- I don't know if it was a station or not-- to those railroad cars, which were passenger railroad cars.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they packed us in those cars.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was December.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was very cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The cars weren't heated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "When I say packed, they packed us into those cars.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But anyone who had a suitcase was told that the railroad cars were too small for suitcases to accommodate them, that they had a freight car in which they were going to load those suitcases into.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And at our destinations, we would get our suitcases back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now, whatever belongings, worldly belongings, we had, we had to give up to be put into the railroad car, into the freight car, which supposedly was at the end of the train.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] Just the thought of it, of thinking back of it-- and I haven't thought of this particular event in a long, long time.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It just-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] --just--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Seeing my parents, and seeing my aunts, and seeing my sister, and other people being in that railroad car, packed in sardines, cold-- destination unknown; even I then, as a child of 14 years, I think that was the first time where it really bothered me-- sunk into my mind-- into my head, where are they taking you?",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where are you going?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What's it going to be?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How much worse can it be than what you have gone through?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's probably going to be better.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It has to be better.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
